casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellant, v. Dempsey, Appellee.

[Cite as State v. Dempsey (1998), 83 Ohio St.3d 107.]

(No. 98-7 Submitted August 19, 1998 Decided September 16, 1998.) Stephanie Tubbs Jones, Cuyahoga County Prosecuting Attorney, L. Christopher Frey and Arthur A. Elkins, Assistant Prosecuting Attorneys, for appellant. Philip J. Korey, for appellee.

*108The judgment of the court of appeals is reversed on the authority of State v. Rush (1998), 83 Ohio St.3d 53, 697 N.E.2d 634.

Moyer, C,J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
